T1  - Principles-Based Standards and Earnings Attributes
AU  - Folsom, David
AU  - Hribar, Paul
AU  - Mergenthaler, Richard D.
AU  - Peterson, Kyle
Y1  - 2016/06/27
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2017/08/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2016.2465
